ss-functional teams to translate business requirements into technical specifications.</li>\n  <li>Execute version control processes and maintain code integrity within a collaborative workflow.</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot, debug, and upgrade existing systems to ensure high reliability and performance.</li>\n  <li>Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code following industry best practices.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Stacks:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Next.js, HTML5, CSS3, and modern JavaScript</li>\n  <li>Golang (Go)</li>\n  <li>PostgreSQL, MongoDB, or other relational/NoSQL databases</li>\n  <li>RESTful API design and integration</li>\n  <li>Git (GitHub/GitLab/Bitbucket)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you're passionate about developing scalable web solutions and ready to grow with us, let’s join our team and Apply Now! </p>\n<p><br></p>"}
