gan:</p>\n<p>    * ISO 8583 / ISO 20022 (nilai plus)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Leadership &amp; Strategic Skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>* Mampu mengubah kebutuhan bisnis menjadi roadmap teknologi</p>\n<p>* Strong stakeholder management (C-level sampai engineer)</p>\n<p>* Pengalaman memimpin design authority / architecture board</p>\n<p>* Decision making berbasis trade-off (cost vs performance vs risk)</p>\n<p>* Mentoring dan membangun capability tim</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Experience Requirements</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>* 4-10+ tahun pengalaman di IT</p>\n<p>* 1-2+ tahun sebagai Solution Architect / Lead Engineer</p>\n<p>* Pengalaman langsung di industri perbankan / financial services</p>\n<p>* Pernah handle sistem dengan high traffic &amp; critical SLA</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Deliverables</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>* Enterprise / Domain Architecture Blueprint</p>\n<p>* High Level Design (HLD) lintas sistem</p>\n<p>* Architecture decision record (ADR)</p>\n<p>* Technology roadmap</p>\n<p>* Governance guideline &amp; standard</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>⸻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>    * TOGAF / Zachman</p>\n<p>    * AWS / Azure Solutions Architect Professional</p>\n<p>* Pengalaman:</p>\n<p>    * Core banking modernization</p>\n<p>    * Cloud migration skala besar</p>\n<p>    * Open banking / API ecosystem</p>"}
