n\n<p><strong>Qualification</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Undergraduate GPA 3.0 or higher</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates or candidates with 1-2 years of experience are welcome to apply</li>\n  <li>Active and likes to communicate with people</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, independent, and hard-working</li>\n  <li>Strong reasoning, logic, and analysis skills</li>\n  <li>Enjoy travelling to places on the job</li>\n  <li>Ability to communicate in Sundanese is a plus</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>BENEFITS</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Competitive monthly salary</li>\n  <li>Merit-based promotions</li>\n  <li>Annual paid leave</li>\n  <li>13th-month bonus</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>HOW TO APPLY</strong></p>\n<p>Submit the below items via email to christine@deliveree.com - If you submit all the required materials and your qualifications fit our search, you will hear back from us within 24 hours.</p>\n<ol><li>Brief cover email</li>\n  <li>PDF resume</li>\n  <li>Completed pre-interview form: https://dlvr.ee/YoungProfessionals</li>\n  <li>University grades or transcript</li>\n  <li>Include ‘Fleet Acquisition’ in the subject line</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
