esses and accounting policies to strengthen internal controls.</li>\n  <li><strong>Prepare supporting data financial statements in a timely manner.</strong></li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate and organized bookkeeping records.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and record budget realization across projects and departments.</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper integration of approval systems into the accounting system.</li>\n</ul>"}
