d meet deadlines.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>What You Will Get</strong></p>\n<p>Besides remuneration and benefits, we also notice other factors that might interest you. CAKAP is an edutech company: we care about education and its impact on others. Elevating people’s lives through education is our objective. Not only for students, but we also attempt to carry out this idea in our team. Therefore, we encourage people who are excited in education and language to join us.</p>\n<p>As we are a startup company, you will learn many things regarding fast-paced culture and improve your adaptability skills. Discussions between low, middle, and high levels often happen; hence you will develop your sensitivity in analyzing surroundings from many layers.<br></p>\n<p><strong>Connect with Us</strong></p>\n<p>Make yourself updated with Cakap &amp; Cakap Squad activities by follow our social media at:</p>\n<p>Instagram: @lifeatcakap @cakapcom</p>\n<p>Twitter : @cakapcom</p>\n<p>Tiktok : @cakapcom</p>\n<p>LinkedIn:Cakap</p>\n<p>谢谢大家xièxiè dàjiā!</p>\n<p><br></p>"}
