</p>\n<p>• Build and maintain relationship with internal and external parties related to accreditation process</p>\n<p>Monitoring &amp; Evaluation Activities:</p>\n<p>• Analyze and report BINUS @Campus performance according to agreed standards and ensure that it’s aligned with assigned strategies</p>\n<p>• Propose changes for reporting systems in order to streamline procedures, improve productivity, and quality</p>\n<p>• Co-ordinate timely and accurate provision of performance data in relation to Key Performance Indicators</p>\n<p>• Ensure performance data is used to assess, review and monitor performance across the unit and identify areas for improvement</p>\n<p>• Co-ordinate and provide performance data for strategic and operational planning</p>\n<p>• Analyze and review effective systems to capture, store and analyse information and produce reports</p>\n<p>• Analyze detailed methodologies and tools and to ensure a good fit for monitoring performance indicators </p>\n<p>• Ensure the effectiveness of liaison between departments in relation to data collection, storage and performance management</p>\n<p>• Liaise and communicate between departments to ensure a good flow of accurate and timely information</p>\n<p>• Assist in reporting of the Monitoring &amp; evaluation activities</p>\n<p>Business Process &amp; Standard Activities:</p>\n<p>• Coordinate overall documents and activities related to Quality Management System in BINUS @Campus </p>\n<p>• Conduct performance analysis by having statistic measurement and other analytical methods</p>\n<p>• Prepare analysis report that needed by management to review organization objectives according review meeting results</p>\n<p>• Coordinate and summarize complaint handling report (complaints from overall stakeholder: students, parents, lecturers and staffs)</p>\n<p>• Coordinate with all units in BINUS @Campus to ensure all processes have run according standard procedure</p>\n<p>• Identify business process in all units in BINUS @Campus and conduct business process analysis to maximize it</p>\n<p>• Review and suggest improvement to maximize the business process</p>\n<p>• Coordinate with all units to collect periodic report and prepare data and periodic report making</p>\n<p>• Verify poor performance and improve the process by having corrective actions and ensure corrective actions have been implemented by related units</p>\n<p>• Analyze customer satisfaction results</p>\n<p>• Ensure timely measurement/survey process implementation</p>\n<p>• Receive complaints from stakeholders and coordinate with related Units to solve the complaints</p>\n<p>• Conduct reoccurrence complaints analysis, analyze report and monitor follow up the process to end reoccurrence</p>\n<p>Quality Assurance System: </p>\n<p>• Prepare, control, and coordinate implementation of quality assurance system documents in BINUS @Campus </p>\n<p>• Coordinate with related units in BINUS @Campus to fulfill the requirements of ISO 9000 or more update version </p>\n<p>• Prepare and Conduct Internal audit activities and management review meeting (schedule, supporting documents and implementation)</p>\n<p>• Monitor Internal Audit process implementation</p>\n<p>• Coordinate with other Units and Auditor to execute internal audit</p>\n<p>• Provide audit finding reports to management in BINUS @Campus to fulfill ISO 9000 requirements</p>\n<p>• Design quality system documents and forms (in Bahasa and English)</p>\n<p>• Design procedures and forms in standard format</p>\n<p>• Conduct Quality objectives measurement process</p>\n<p>• Respond, review, upload quality system documents that come from other Units</p>\n<p>• Ensure that all findings in Internal audit process has follow up actions</p>\n<p>• Ensure that reoccurrence audit findings will decrease in the next period</p>\n<p>Management Support Activities:</p>\n<p>• In Coordination with Rector’s Office, analyze, synthesize and prepare PI and KPI for all units under BINUS @Campus and support for the finalization of the PIs and KPIs documents.</p>\n<p>• In Coordination with Finance Division, analyze, synthesize and prepare annual budget for all units under BINUS @Campusand support for the finalization of the approved documents.</p>\n<p>• On behalf of Campus Director, prepare routine reports to the Rector of Binus University and Yayasan Bina Nusantara.</p>\n<p>• Provide Report to direct Supervisor </p>\n<p>• Monitor the overall documentation process in related area</p>\n<p>• Suggest improvement process related to activities in area of responsibilities (especially related to time concern, effort and cost) </p>\n<p>• Perform activities related to Quality Management System</p>\n<p>• Perform additional tasks as required by Direct Supervisor</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• Minimum Bachelor's Degree in Management or related field</p>\n<p>• Minimum 4 years of working experience</p>\n<p>• Strong knowledge on Education Operational Management</p>\n<p>• Have skills in Business Process &amp; ISO</p>\n<p>• Willing to be placed in Medan</p>\n<p><br></p>"}
