kflows: qualification, follow-up, scheduling, knowledge systems) </li>\n  <li><strong>Tech Marketing Manager</strong> (proof &amp; trust: narratives, case studies, credibility) </li>\n  <li><strong>Tech Growth Manager</strong> (distribution: LinkedIn Ads, Google Search Ads, retargeting, outbound) </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Scale distribution where buyers actually convert </p>\n<ul><li>Make Sagara appear repeatedly in front of the right decision-makers </li>\n  <li>Build performance loops across:       \n    <ul><li><strong>LinkedIn Ads</strong> (primary B2B channel) </li>\n      <li><strong>Google Search Ads</strong> (capture active intent) </li>\n      <li>Retargeting + outbound to high-fit accounts </li>\n    </ul></li>\n  <li>Run weekly optimization: audiences, creatives, landing pages, conversion rates</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>What “Great” Looks Like </p>\n<p>A great Director of Tech Outsourcing Growth at Sagara:</p>\n<ul><li>Makes Sagara <strong>easy to understand, easy to trust, and easy to buy</strong> </li>\n  <li>Creates a predictable pipeline engine (not sporadic wins)</li>\n  <li>Improves conversion by building proof, not hype </li>\n  <li>Builds campaign systems that keep working without daily heroics </li>\n  <li>Treats growth as an operational discipline: measurement, iteration, accountability</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Requirements (Must-Have) </p>\n<ul><li>Strong experience building <strong>B2B growth/pipeline</strong> for services (tech outsourcing, software dev, consulting, SaaS with services motion) </li>\n  <li>Ability to lead cross-functional teams and align them to one outcome </li>\n  <li>Proven ability to build trust assets that increase conversion (case studies, proof, narratives, objections) </li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of performance channels:       \n    <ul><li>LinkedIn Ads, Search Ads, retargeting, outbound systems </li>\n    </ul></li>\n  <li>High execution discipline: weekly rhythm, KPI-driven decisions, strong prioritization </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Nice-to-Have </p>\n<ul><li>Experience in outsourcing/agency delivery environments (SLA, squads, client retention) </li>\n  <li>Comfortable with AI-native workflows and automation systems for qualification &amp; follow-up </li>\n  <li>Familiarity with CRM + WhatsApp-based follow-up flows</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
