ct backlog (BRD/PRD translation into user stories)</p>\n<p>• Collaborate with stakeholders and ability to ensure requirements into well-defined user</p>\n<p>stories using BDD / Gherkin language</p>\n<p>• Ensure requirements are complete, clear, and ready for development</p>\n<p>• Facilitate discussions to align requirements, design, and delivery</p>\n<p>• Ensure solution meets business objectives and timelines</p>\n<p>• Ensure compliance with security, scalability, and performance standards</p>\n<p>• Conduct design reviews and provide recommendations</p>\n<p>• Identify risks and propose mitigation strategies</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>• WIlling to contractual (6 months)</p>\n<p>• Proven experience as System Analyst / Solution Architect / Technical Architect (3+</p>\n<p>years)</p>\n<p>• Strong experience with ArchiMate modeling</p>\n<p>• Strong analytical skills</p>\n<p>• Hands-on experience creating:</p>\n<p>o Sequence diagrams</p>\n<p>o ERD / data modeling</p>\n<p>o Technical Solution Design (TSD) documents</p>\n<p>• Experience with API design, microservices, and system integration</p>\n<p>• Strong understanding of system architecture patterns (event-driven, distributed</p>\n<p>systems)</p>\n<p>• Experience acting as Product Owner or working closely with PO</p>\n<p>• Strong experience in writing behavior-driven user stories (BDD) / Gherkin language</p>\n<p>using to ensure clarity, testability, and alignment between business and engineering</p>\n<p>teams</p>\n<p>• Familiar with Agile / Scrum methodology</p>\n<p>• Experience in financial services / lending / fintech</p>\n<p>• Familiar with tools like:</p>\n<p>o Visual Paradigm</p>\n<p>o Draw.io</p>\n<p>o BPMN</p>\n<p>o Jira / Confluence</p>\n<p>• Experience with Kafka, CDC, or event streaming architecture</p>\n<p><br></p>"}
