{"job_title": "Full Stack Developer", "job_location": "Jakarta - Indonesia", "job_department": "Software Engineer", "job_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs/b5d30232-acc3-45b5-a2fa-14d8f4efb997", "first_seen": "2026-04-21 16:03:37", "base_salary": "9000000", "job_type": "Full-time", "job_level": "3 - 7 years", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-05-06 02:47:15", "last_seen": "2026-04-06 02:47:15", "is_active": "True", "company": "Automata Neo Solutions", "company_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/companies/automata-neo-solutions", "job_board": "Tech in Asia Jobs", "job_board_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs", "job_age": "recent", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "Full Stack Developer Software Engineer <p>We are looking for a skilled <strong>Full Stack Developer</strong> with 3–5 years of experience who embraces modern development workflows — including <strong>AI-assisted coding</strong> — to build fast, scalable, and high-quality products for Australian clients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You’ll work in a collaborative, async-friendly environment where speed, experimentation, and clean execution matter. If you enjoy building with tools like Claude, Supabase, and modern frameworks, this role is for you.</p>\n<p><br>\nKey Responsibilities</p>\n<ul><li>Build and ship full-stack applications end-to-end<br>\n </li>\n  <li>Use AI tools (e.g., Claude) to accelerate development, debugging, and prototyping<br>\n </li>\n  <li>Develop frontend interfaces using modern frameworks (Next JS)<br>\n </li>\n  <li>Build backend services, APIs, and integrations<br>\n </li>\n  <li>Work closely with Australian clients and internal teams<br>\n  </li>\n  <li>Ensure code quality, performance, and scalability<br>\n </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Tech Stack / Tools</strong>\n</p>\n\n<ul><li>Frontend: Next JS<br>\n </li>\n  <li>Backend: Node.js / Laravel / serverless functions<br>\n </li>\n  <li>Database &amp; Backend-as-a-Service: Supabase / Firebase<br>\n </li>\n  <li>AI Tools: Claude, ChatGPT,