ecific area. To make it easier, there are:</p>\n<ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in computer science, computer engineering, or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 1 years of working experience in Quality assurance, Quality Testing, or any related field.</li>\n  <li>Ability to analyze and decompose complex software and design test strategy.</li>\n  <li>A troubleshooter with eagle eyes: you put perfection as essential in our web application.</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge in Java and MySQL.</li>\n  <li>Experience with Test Automation with Selenium is a huge plus.<br>\n </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>What You Will Get</strong></p>\n<p>Besides remuneration and benefits, we also notice other factors that might interest you. CAKAP is an edutech company: we care about education and its impact on others. Elevating people’s lives through education is our objective. Not only for students, but we also attempt to carry out this idea in our team. Therefore, we encourage people who are excited in education and language to join us.As we are a startup company, you will learn many things regarding fast-paced culture and improve your adaptability skill. Discussions between low, middle, and high levels often happen; hence you will develop your sensitivity in analyzing surroundings from many layers.</p>\n<p><br></p>"}
