guring, optimizing, and maintaining Virtual Private Servers (VPS) for Treasury operational needs.</li>\n  <li>Technical Support: Performing rapid actions (restart/reconfiguration) in the event of server or application disruptions during operational hours.</li>\n  <li>Shift Reports: Documenting and reporting transaction activities and technical issues that occur during the shift.</li>\n  <li>Issue Escalation: Serve as the first line of defense in detecting system anomalies and coordinate promptly with the IT or liquidity teams in the event of downtime.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
