{"job_title": "Product Manager", "job_location": "Tangerang - Indonesia", "job_department": "Project & Product Management", "job_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs/54c54eef-6b8a-4ed2-8efd-2c8d583d5eb5", "first_seen": "2026-04-21 16:03:37", "base_salary": "0", "job_type": "Full-time", "job_level": "4 - 8 years", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-04-26 08:34:11", "last_seen": "2026-03-27 08:34:11", "is_active": "True", "company": "Cakap", "company_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/companies/cakap", "job_board": "Tech in Asia Jobs", "job_board_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs", "job_age": "old", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "Product Manager Project & Product Management <p>Responsibilities\n</p>\n\n<ol><li>End-to-End Product Ownership: Own a specific product or core feature set, driving it from continuous discovery to successful delivery and iteration.</li>\n  <li>Outcome-Driven Strategy: Execute product strategy by defining clear success metrics (e.g., OKRs), prioritizing features based on user value, and managing an adaptable backlog.</li>\n  <li>AI &amp; Innovation Integration: Identify opportunities to integrate AI/ML capabilities (such as personalized learning paths or automated feedback) to solve user problems and enhance the educational experience.</li>\n  <li>Cross-Functional Leadership: Collaborate deeply with engineering, design, data, and business units to align product development with overarching business goals.</li>\n  <li>Data &amp; AI-Augmented Analytics: Analyze product performance metrics and user feedback, leveraging modern AI data analysis tools to rapidly synthesize qualitative data and uncover behavioral trends.</li>\n  <li>Market Intelligence: Conduct deep market research and competitive analysis, keeping a pulse on emerging EdTech trends and AI advancements to inform the roadmap.</li>\n  <li>Stakeholder Alignment: Create, present, and advocate for product roadmaps, ensuring transparency and alignment across the organization.</li>\n</ol><p>Qualification\n</p>\n\n<ol><li>Experience: 3-6 years in product management or a closely related field, with a proven track record of shipping impactful, user-centric products.</li>\n  <li>Education: Bachelor’s degree in business, design, engineering, or equivalent experience.</li>\n  <li>AI Literacy: Demonstrated understanding of how to leverage AI tools for daily productivity (e.g., prompt engineering, automated research) and a solid grasp of how to integrate AI capabilities into digital products ethically.</li>\n  <li>Agile Expertise: Deep knowledge of modern, agile product development practices, with the ability to adapt frameworks to team needs.</li>\n  <li>Leadership &amp; Communication: Strong ability to lead by influence, remove friction, drive collaboration, and communicate complex concepts clearly.</li>\n  <li>Problem-Solving: Exceptional analytical skills with a data-informed approach to decision-making.</li>\n  <li>Language: Fluency in both written and spoken English.</li>\n  <li>Mission-Driven: A strong, genuine interest in creating lasting social impact through Indonesia's education ecosystem.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><strong>Connect with Us</strong>  Make yourself updated with Cakap &amp; Cakap Squad Activities by follow our social media at:</p>\n<ul><li>Instagram: @lifeatcakap @cakapcom</li>\n  <li>Twitter: @cakapcom</li>\n  <li>Tiktok: @cakapcom</li>\n  <li>LinkedIn: linkedin.com/company/cakap</li>\n</ul>"}
