reed standards and ensure that it’s aligned with assigned strategies</p>\n<p>•\tPropose changes for reporting systems in order to streamline procedures, improve productivity, and quality</p>\n<p>•\tProvide performance data for strategic and operational planning</p>\n<p>•\tLiaise between departments in relation to data collection, storage and performance management</p>\n<p>•\tProvide report on monitoring &amp; evaluation activities</p>\n<p>Business Process and Standard Activities:</p>\n<p>•\tEnsure compliance process implementation in BINUS @Campus</p>\n<p>•\tOrganize customer satisfaction survey and provide result review</p>\n<p>•\tConduct survey process implementation according to agreed timeline</p>\n<p>•\tReceive complaints from stakeholders and communicate with related Units for solutions</p>\n<p>•\tConduct reoccurrence complaints analysis and provide report</p>\n<p>Quality Assurance System:</p>\n<p>•\tImplement quality assurance system documents in BINUS @Campus</p>\n<p>•\tCommunicate with related units in BINUS @Campus to fulfill the requirements of ISO 9000 or more update version</p>\n<p>•\tOrganize Internal audit activities and management review meeting (schedule, supporting documents and implementation)</p>\n<p>•\tMonitor Internal Audit process implementation</p>\n<p>•\tCoordinate with other Units and Auditor to execute internal audit</p>\n<p>•\tProvide data for audit finding reports to management in BINUS @Campus to fulfill ISO 9000 requirements</p>\n<p>•\tEnsure performance data is ready to be used to assess, review and monitor performance across the unit and identify areas for improvement</p>\n<p>•\tFollow up internal audit findings and ensure action from related units</p>\n<p>Management Support Activities:</p>\n<p>•\tProvide Report to direct Supervisor</p>\n<p>•\tSuggest improvement process related to activities in area of responsibilities (especially related to time concern, effort and cost)</p>\n<p>•\tPerform activities related to Quality Management System</p>\n<p>•\tPerform additional tasks related to key responsibilities as required by Direct Supervisor</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>•\tMinimum Bachelor's Degree in Management or related field</p>\n<p>•\tMinimum 2 years of working experience</p>\n<p>•\tHave skills in Business Process &amp; ISO</p>\n<p>•\tWilling to be placed in Semarang</p>\n<p><br></p>"}
{"job_title": "HR Service Delivery Consultant", "job_location": "Jakarta - Indonesia", "job_department": "Human Resources", "job_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs/3d5e0a26-affa-4a9c-95b5-259e33d16810", "first_seen": "2026-04-21 16:03:37", "base_salary": "0", "job_type": "Full-time", "job_level": "3 - 15 years", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-04-25 13:00:34", "last_seen": "2026-03-26 13:00:34", "is_active": "True", "company": "PT BIPO Service Indonesia", "company_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/companies/pt-bipo-service-indonesia", "job_board": "Tech in Asia Jobs", "job_board_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs", "job_age": "old", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "HR Service Delivery Consultant Human Resources <p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p>\n<p>The HR Service Delivery Consultant is responsible for delivering end-to-end HR operational services to assigned clients or business units, ensuring accuracy, compliance, and service excellence. This role acts as the primary point of contact for HR service delivery, managing daily HR operations, statutory compliance, payroll coordination, and client communication.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p><u>HR Service Delivery &amp; Operations</u></p>\n<ul><li>Deliver day-to-day HR operational services in accordance with agreed Service Level Agreements (SLAs).</li>\n  <li>Manage employee lifecycle processes: onboarding, contract administration, employee data changes, resignations, and terminations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure accurate and timely HR administration and documentation.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Payroll &amp; Statutory Coordination</u></p>\n<ul><li>Coordinate payroll processing with internal payroll teams.</li>\n  <li>Oversee statutory compliance including BPJS Kesehatan, BPJS Ketenagakerjaan, and other local labor requirements.</li>\n  <li>Review payroll and statutory reports for accuracy prior to submission.</li>\n  <li>Client &amp; Stakeholder Management</li>\n  <li>Act as the main point of contact for clients on HR operational matters.</li>\n  <li>Respond to client inquiries professionally and within agreed timelines.</li>\n  <li>Provide clear explanations and guidance to clients regarding HR processes, policies, and local labor practices.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Compliance &amp; Risk Management</u></p>\n<ul><li>Ensure HR processes comply with Indonesian labor law and statutory regulations.</li>\n  <li>Identify potential compliance risks and escalate issues appropriately.</li>\n  <li>Support internal and external audits related to HR, payroll, and statutory matters.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Reporting &amp; Documentation</u></p>\n<ul><li>Prepare Payroll Reports for clients.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate employee records and HR databases.</li>\n  <li>Track service delivery metrics and client deliverables.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Qualifications &amp; Experience</u></p>\n<ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Human Resources, Business Administration, or related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum [1-2] years of experience in HR operations, service delivery, or HR outsourcing.</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of Indonesian labor law and statutory requirements.</li>\n  <li>Experience handling payroll.</li>\n  <li>Client-facing experience is highly preferred.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Skills &amp; Competencies</u></p>\n<ul><li>Strong communication and stakeholder management skills.</li>\n  <li>Detail-oriented with high accuracy standards.</li>\n  <li>Ability to manage multiple clients and priorities.</li>\n  <li>Problem-solving and analytical thinking.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in MS Excel and HR/payroll systems.</li>\n  <li>Good command of Bahasa Indonesia and English; Mandarin proficiency is an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Behavioral Competencies</u></p>\n<ul><li>Customer-focused mindset</li>\n  <li>High accountability and ownership</li>\n  <li>Professional judgment and discretion</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under pressure and meet deadlines</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
