y before deployment.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Project management experience in a tech company minimum </li>\n  <li>Proven ability to work with cross-functional teams</li>\n  <li>Excellent troubleshooting, debugging, documentation, and communication skills. </li>\n  <li>Experience seeing projects through the full lifecycle. </li>\n  <li>Skilled in managing multiple short to medium-term projects simultaneously</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of programming concepts</li>\n  <li>Understanding of API integration principles</li>\n  <li>Experience working with APIs and using platforms like Postman or Insomnia</li>\n  <li>Proven experience collaborating with engineers</li>\n  <li>Understand the usage and creation of Project Requirement Documents (PRDs)</li>\n  <li>Willingness to work in multiple time zones as our clients operate around the world.</li>\n  <li>Fluent in written and spoken Business English.</li>\n  <li>(Good to have) Familiarity with Python programming language. </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Why Jublia:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>This is going to be a learning experience like no other! Be prepared to be challenged in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Our global clientele will challenge your thinking about matchmaking in different geographical cultures, across more than 40 different industry sectors. </li>\n  <li>The products you build will be used by leading B2B events with over 100,000 unique users monthly. </li>\n  <li>We take pride in our coding and want you to do the same. Together, we are all about shipping clean and efficient code. </li>\n  <li>We are detail-oriented, especially with solving issues. We never do shoddy patching of codes. </li>\n  <li>We take your career growth and skills development to heart. We strive to help you lead a professional and personal life with us.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Our Great Range of Perks:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>We are mostly remote, where you can work from the comfort of your home, and enjoy flexible working time.</li>\n  <li>Competitive range of health benefits to support your well beings.</li>\n  <li>A generous budget to spend on setting up your home office or to support your continuous learning.</li>\n  <li>Additional end of year paid holiday leave entitlement besides the common yearly paid leave. Spend the rest of the year with your beloved or enjoy the time by yourself.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
