{"job_title": "Data Analyst", "job_location": "Tangerang - Indonesia", "job_department": "Data & Analytics", "job_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs/5831384c-a778-4b9e-860e-e63d955544a4", "first_seen": "2026-04-21 16:03:37", "base_salary": "0", "job_type": "Full-time", "job_level": "1 - 4 years", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-04-14 16:12:09", "last_seen": "2026-03-15 16:12:09", "is_active": "True", "company": "Cakap", "company_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/companies/cakap", "job_board": "Tech in Asia Jobs", "job_board_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs", "job_age": "expired", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "Data Analyst Data & Analytics <p><strong>What You Will Do</strong></p>\n<p>We are seeking a highly motivated and detail-oriented Data Analyst to join our team. The successful candidate will play a critical role in transforming raw data into actionable insights to support decision-making across the organization. You will collaborate with cross-functional teams to identify opportunities, solve business problems, and enhance operational efficiency.</p>\n<p>Your key responsibilities will include:</p>\n<ul><li>Collaborating with the operations team to gain a deep understanding of business processes and operational workflows.</li>\n  <li>Partnering with the technology team to understand the database schema and ensure effective data extraction.</li>\n  <li>Automating weekly and monthly operational reports to improve efficiency and accuracy.</li>\n  <li>Designing and developing dashboards and visualizations using BI tools such as Metabase, Power BI, or Tableau.</li>\n  <li>Writing and optimizing complex SQL queries to retrieve and analyze data from multiple sources.</li>\n  <li>Conducting in-depth analysis of customer and teacher behaviors to uncover trends, patterns, and improvement opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Driving projects aimed at improving conversion rates, including analysis of lead-to-purchase funnels and customer demographics.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring data integrity, consistency, and accuracy across reports and dashboards.</li>\n  <li>Presenting insights and recommendations clearly to both technical and non-technical stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Supporting strategic initiatives by providing data-driven inputs to product, marketing, and operations teams.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Requirements and Qualifications</strong></p>\n<p>To succeed in this role, you should meet the following qualifications:</p>\n<ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Statistics, Mathematics, Economics, or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum of 3 years of professional experience in data analytics, business intelligence, or a related discipline.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in SQL and experience working with relational databases.</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience with BI and visualization tools such as Metabase, Power BI, or Tableau.</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, with the ability to translate complex data into actionable insights.</li>\n  <li>Excellent documentation skills, with the ability to clearly communicate methodologies and findings.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and collaboration skills, especially in a multicultural and cross-functional environment.</li>\n  <li>Fluency in both written and spoken English.</li>\n  <li>A proactive mindset with the ability to manage multiple priorities and work independently.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with the startup ecosystem and interest in contributing to a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Passion for creating social impact, particularly in advancing education in Indonesia</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Connect with us:</strong></p>\n<p>Make yourself updated with Cakap &amp; Cakap Squad activities by follow our social media at:</p>\n<ul><li>IG: @lifeatcakap @cakapcom</li>\n  <li>Twitter: @cakapcom</li>\n  <li>TikTok: @cakapcom</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
