il testing</p>\n<p>7. Berkolaborasi dengan developer untuk investigasi dan reproduksi bug</p>\n<p>8. Mendukung proses regression testing sebelum deployment</p>\n<p>9. Berkontribusi pada automated testing menggunakan tools seperti Playwright / Supertest Primary Qualifications (these qualifications are necessary to perform job)</p>"}
{"job_title": "Functional Consultant for Microsoft Dynamic 365 (Sales and Customer Service)", "job_location": "Jakarta - Indonesia", "job_department": "Enterprise Software & Systems", "job_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs/8ebf5615-a0ad-47b4-84c2-1c31727e0cdb", "first_seen": "2026-04-21 16:03:37", "base_salary": "18000000", "job_type": "Full-time", "job_level": "4 - 15 years", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-04-10 10:34:18", "last_seen": "2026-03-11 10:34:18", "is_active": "True", "company": "Romulus Digital", "company_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/companies/romulus-digital", "job_board": "Tech in Asia Jobs", "job_board_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs", "job_age": "expired", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "Functional Consultant for Microsoft Dynamic 365 (Sales and Customer Service) Enterprise Software & Systems <p><strong>About Us: <br></strong>Romulus Digital is a dynamic company serving regional clients, including those in Singapore. We connect local talent with global opportunities, specializing in delivering innovative solutions and resource augmentation to help our clients reach their business objectives. We are currently looking for a skilled Functional Consultant for Dynamic 365 (Sales and Customer Service) to join our team and play a key role in our ongoing success.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Position Summary: </strong></p>\n<p>We are seeking a highly experienced and motivated Functional Consultant for Dynamic 365 (Sales and Customer Service) professional to join our team. In this role, you will be responsible for implementing, customizing, and supporting Dynamic 365 solutions, with a focus on Sales and Customer Service modules. You will work closely with clients and internal teams to understand business requirements, design solutions, and ensure successful project delivery. This is a full-time position offering the opportunity to make a significant impact on our clients' business processes and overall success.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Analyze client business requirements and translate them into effective Dynamic 365 solutions within the Sales and Customer Service modules.</li>\n  <li>Design, configure, and customize Dynamic 365 Sales and Customer Service modules to meet specific client needs.</li>\n  <li>Lead and participate in the implementation, testing, and deployment of Dynamic 365 solutions.</li>\n  <li>Provide expert-level support and troubleshooting for Dynamic 365 users.</li>\n  <li>Develop and maintain comprehensive documentation, including design specifications, configuration settings, and user manuals.</li>\n  <li>Stay up-to-date with the latest Dynamic 365 features and updates, and proactively identify opportunities to leverage new capabilities.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including developers, consultants, and project managers, to ensure seamless project execution.</li>\n  <li>Conduct training sessions for end-users to promote effective utilization of Dynamic 365 Sales and Customer Service functionalities.</li>\n  <li>Participate in pre-sales activities, including solution demonstrations and proposal development.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Required Skills &amp; Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Extensive experience working with Dynamic 365, with a focus on Sales and Customer Service modules.</li>\n  <li>Proven ability to analyze business requirements and design effective solutions within Dynamic 365.</li>\n  <li>Strong configuration and customization skills within Dynamic 365, including workflows, business rules, and security roles.</li>\n  <li>Experience with data migration and integration between Dynamic 365 and other systems.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, interpersonal, and presentation skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team.</li>\n  <li>Strong problem-solving and analytical skills.</li>\n  <li>A proven track record of successful Dynamic 365 implementations.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Preferred Skills &amp; Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Experience with Power Platform (Power Apps, Power Automate, Power BI).</li>\n  <li>Dynamic 365 certifications.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of industry best practices for CRM and customer service.</li>\n  <li>Experience with agile development methodologies.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Opportunity to work on impactful projects with regional or international exposure.</li>\n  <li>Competitive compensation package aligned with skills and experience.</li>\n  <li>Comprehensive health coverage and wellness support programs.</li>\n  <li>Access to training, certifications, and continuous learning opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Modern work tools and collaborative environment that values innovation.</li>\n  <li>Flexible or hybrid work options promoting work-life balance.</li>\n  <li>Regular team-building activities and company-wide events.</li>\n  <li>Supportive, inclusive, and growth-oriented workplace culture.</li>\n  <li>Recognition for contributions and career advancement opportunities.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>"}
