saging and enhance the user experience</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>What you will get</p>\n<p>CAKAP is an edutech company: we care about education and its impact on others. Elevating people’s lives through education is our objective. Not only for students, but we also attempt to carry out this idea in our team. Therefore, we encourage people who are excited about education and language to join us. As we are a startup company, you will learn many things regarding fast-paced culture and improve your adaptability skills. Discussions between low, middle, and high levels often happen; hence you will develop your sensitivity in analyzing surroundings from many layers.</p>\n<p>Connect with Us  </p>\n<p>Make yourself updated with Cakap &amp; Cakap Squad activities by following our social media at:</p>\n<ul><li>Instagram: @lifeatcakap @cakapcom</li>\n  <li>Twitter: @cakapcom</li>\n  <li>Tiktok: @cakapcom</li>\n  <li>LinkedIn: linkedin.com/company/cakap</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>谢谢大家</p>\n<p>xièxiè dàjiā!</p>\n<p><br></p>"}
