{"job_title": "Senior Data Engineer", "job_location": "Jakarta - Indonesia", "job_department": "Data & Analytics", "job_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs/38bf430e-77e9-4e8e-9a48-39cfed21c973", "first_seen": "2026-04-21 16:03:37", "base_salary": "10000000", "job_type": "Contract", "job_level": "5 - 6 years", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-03-28 07:52:29", "last_seen": "2026-02-26 07:52:29", "is_active": "True", "company": "PT Tiga Daya Digital Indonesia", "company_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/companies/pt-tiga-daya-digital-indonesia", "job_board": "Tech in Asia Jobs", "job_board_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs", "job_age": "expired", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "Senior Data Engineer Data & Analytics <p><strong>Job Description</strong>\n</p>\n\n<ol><li>Develop and plan work activities to ensure timely and structured project execution.</li>\n  <li>Design and build streaming pipelines for real-time data processing.</li>\n  <li>Develop and maintain data marts to support reporting and dashboard requirements.</li>\n  <li>Collect, sort, clean, and manage data to ensure accuracy and reliability.</li>\n  <li>Perform data analysis and present insights and findings to relevant teams.</li>\n  <li>Manage data transfer processes (including tally data) from transactional databases to the data warehouse.</li>\n  <li>Administer and manage server job schedulers to ensure smooth data processing operations.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to identify and resolve technical issues on both backend and frontend systems.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and submit monthly work progress reports</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><strong>Minimum Qualifications</strong>\n</p>\n\n<ol><li>Experienced in Data Engineer role <strong>minimum for 5 years</strong></li>\n  <li>Proficient in <strong>Python</strong> for data processing &amp; automation.</li>\n  <li>Advanced <strong>SQL skills</strong> (subquery, Row_Number, Rank, Partition By, Indexing, Explain Plan, dan Query Tuning, Stored Procedures, Triggers, View, Materialize View, Constraints, indexing, query optimization)</li>\n  <li>Strong hands-on experience with: MySQL, PostgreSQL, Oracle, <strong>Snowflake</strong>, Handling structured &amp; unstructured data</li>\n  <li>Experience in Distributed Data Storage Systems (partitioned data storage, sorting key, SerDes, data replication, caching and persistence)</li>\n  <li>Distributed Data Processing Systems (partitioning, predicate pushdown, sort by partition, maintaining size of shuffle blocks, window function, leveraging all cores and memory available in the cluster to improve concurrency)</li>\n  <li>Stream Data Processing (Real-time, Stream and Batch Processing)</li>\n  <li>Experinced in using tools such as:</li>\n</ol>\n\n<ul><li>Data Pipelines and Automation (Airbyte)</li>\n  <li>Data ingestion in Message Queues</li>\n  <li>Data Wrangling operations – Pandas,numpy,re d. Data Scraping – requests/BeautifulSoup/lxml/Scrapy</li>\n  <li>Interacting with External APIs and other Data Sources, Logging</li>\n  <li>Parallel processing Libraries – Dask, Multiprocessing</li>\n  <li>Data engineering tools (Apache Kafka, Apache Airflow)</li>\n  <li>Cloud Native Technologies (Serverless Computing, Virtual Instances, Containering Docker, Orchestration Kubernetes)</li>\n  <li>Data Visualization (Qlikview, Tableau)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Full on-site in South Jakarta, Mega Kuningan</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>"}
{"job_title": "Senior Automation Tester", "job_location": "Jakarta - Indonesia", "job_department": "Software Engineer", "job_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs/b3ed0dac-60d9-491f-a2d3-c48c1323a25f", "first_seen": "2026-04-21 16:03:37", "base_salary": "0", "job_type": "Contract", "job_level": "5 - 15 years", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-03-28 05:32:48", "last_seen": "2026-02-26 05:32:48", "is_active": "True", "company": "PT Appfuxion Consulting Indonesia", "company_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/companies/pt-appfuxion-consulting-indonesia", "job_board": "Tech in Asia Jobs", "job_board_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs", "job_age": "expired", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "Senior Automation Tester Software Engineer <p><strong>Job purpose:</strong><br></p>\n<p>Play a critical role in the area of software quality engineering. Responsible primarily to test and automate the tests as part of the CI/CD pipeline. Additionally responsible for promoting knowledge, expertise and standards for modern software testing and QA to ensure the best customer experience for all our digital channels, without compromising the velocity of delivery.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br></p>\n<ul><li>Work in Scrum squad as a specialist QA</li>\n  <li>Assist squad to formulate the definition of done and the acceptance criteria based on the user story/requirements</li>\n  <li>As part of the squad, identify story points based on the QA point of view</li>\n  <li>Design and write test data, test scripts, and test plan </li>\n  <li>Execute manual test during the sprint and create automation test scripts on the subsequent sprint </li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the related team to implement the automated tests as part of the CI/CD pipeline</li>\n  <li>Follow up bugs and ensure all are clean prior to deployment</li>\n  <li>Prepare test artifacts (test result, defect log, sign off) and dashboard (test progress, bugs monitoring) as part of sprint deliverables</li>\n  <li>Able to work as cross cross-functional team to ensure</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>B.S. in Computer Science, Information Systems or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Experience in software testing role</li>\n  <li>Experience in web, mobile and API testing, including verify the messaging log</li>\n  <li>Experience with test automation tools (Katalon Studio, Appium, Selenium)</li>\n  <li>Experience with Cucumber and Gherkin is a huge plus</li>\n  <li>Experience in creation &amp; usage of SQL queries</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
{"job_title": "Junior Accountant", "job_location": "Jakarta - Indonesia", "job_department": "Finance - Legal & Accounting", "job_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs/cd4c724f-3598-4049-b8b3-846520b6754b", "first_seen": "2026-04-21 16:03:37", "base_salary": "6000000", "job_type": "Full-time", "job_level": "1 - 15 years", "job_apply_end_date": "2026-03-27 14:12:56", "last_seen": "2026-02-25 14:12:56", "is_active": "True", "company": "Whitesky Aviation", "company_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/companies/whitesky-aviation", "job_board": "Tech in Asia Jobs", "job_board_url": "https://www.techinasia.com/jobs", "job_age": "expired", "work_arrangement": "On-site", "desc": "Junior Accountant Finance, Legal & Accounting <p><strong>Job Overview</strong></p>\n<p>We are seeking a highly analytical and detail-oriented Junior Accountant to support our finance team in managing financial records, analyzing revenue streams, and ensuring accuracy in reporting. The ideal candidate has strong analytical capability, high work standards, and a deep understanding of accounting systems and tools.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1. Financial Recording &amp; Reporting</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Maintain accurate and timely bookkeeping of daily transactions</li>\n  <li>Prepare journal entries, reconciliations, and supporting schedules</li>\n  <li>Assist in monthly, quarterly, and annual financial closing</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>2. Revenue Analysis &amp; Monitoring</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Analyze revenue across different business lines and service streams</li>\n  <li>Perform revenue reconciliation and variance analysis</li>\n  <li>Monitor billing accuracy and identify discrepancies</li>\n  <li>Support management with financial insights related to revenue performance</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>3. Cost Control &amp; Compliance</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Assist in monitoring operational expenses and cost allocation</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with accounting standards and company policies</li>\n  <li>Support internal and external audit processes</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>4. System &amp; Process Improvement</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Utilize accounting software and financial tools efficiently</li>\n  <li>Maintain organized financial documentation</li>\n  <li>Proactively recommend improvements in reporting and workflow efficiency</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Performance Indicators (KPI)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1.Financial Accuracy &amp; Compliance</strong></p>\n<ul><li>≥ 99% transaction accuracy rate</li>\n  <li>Zero major audit findings attributable to accounting errors</li>\n  <li>Timely completion of monthly closing (within agreed timeline)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>2.Revenue Monitoring</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Accurate reconciliation of revenue across all business lines</li>\n  <li>Timely identification and reporting of revenue discrepancies</li>\n  <li>Clear monthly revenue analysis report submission</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>3.Productivity &amp; Discipline</strong></p>\n<ul><li>On-time submission of reports and assigned deliverables</li>\n  <li>Complete documentation for all financial transactions</li>\n  <li>Responsiveness to cross-department financial inquiries</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>4.Analytical Contribution</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Ability to identify trends, irregularities, and improvement opportunities</li>\n  <li>Contribution to financial insight discussions with senior finance team</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Education</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Accounting or Finance</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Experience</strong></p>\n<ul><li>1–5 years of experience in accounting or finance</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates with strong academic performance are welcome to apply</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Technical Skills</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Strong understanding of accounting principles </li>\n  <li>Proficient in accounting software (e.g., Accurate, SAP, Oracle, or similar)</li>\n  <li>Advanced Excel skills (pivot tables, formulas, data analysis)</li>\n  <li>Comfortable working with financial systems and digital tools</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Core Competencies</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Strong analytical thinking, especially in revenue structure analysis</li>\n  <li>High attention to detail and accuracy</li>\n  <li>Strong sense of responsibility and ownership</li>\n  <li>Structured, organized, and disciplined work habits</li>\n  <li>High personal standards in completing assigned tasks</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under deadlines</li>\n  <li>Integrity and confidentiality</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
