ing For:</strong></p>\n<ul><li><strong>Social-Savvy<br></strong>Deep understanding of Instagram, TikTok, and what makes content go viral.</li>\n  <li><strong>Engaging On-Camera<br></strong>Confident, natural, and expressive when speaking to the camera.</li>\n  <li><strong>Creative &amp; Strategic<br></strong>Strong instincts for what captures attention and drives action.</li>\n  <li><strong>Editing-Skilled<br></strong>Advanced in CapCut or similar mobile editing tools.</li>\n  <li><strong>Self-Starter &amp; Finisher<br></strong>Organized, independent, and responsible from idea to final upload.</li>\n  <li><strong>Performance-Oriented<br></strong>You think beyond likes — and aim for engagement, traffic, and sales.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>You’ll thrive here if:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>You’re not just here to post content — you’re here to grow a brand, get better every week, and turn creative ideas into real impact.</li>\n  <li>You take pride in what you create, you love connecting with people online, and you’re ready to be part of a team that’s building something big — together.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
