ements.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul><li>Available to join early March 2026</li>\n  <li>Industry Experience: Prior experience in the Banking/Fintech industry is highly preferred, specifically with an understanding of web or mobile banking transactions.</li>\n  <li>Technical Stack: Mastery of Java Spring Boot and Rust programming languages.</li>\n  <li>Architecture: Deep understanding of Microservices architecture and design patterns.</li>\n  <li>Database Knowledge: Strong proficiency in PostgreSQL database management and optimization.</li>\n  <li>DevOps Tools: Hands-on experience with CI/CD tools, specifically Bitbucket and Jenkins.</li>\n  <li>Quality Assurance: Proven ability to write and maintain comprehensive Unit Tests.</li>\n  <li>Analytical Skills: Excellent analytical thinking and problem-solving skills to handle complex financial data and system logic.</li>\n  <li>Education: Minimum Bachelor’s Degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or a related field.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
