usiness questions.</li>\n  <li>Communicate with management and stakeholders regularly to share updates and findings.</li>\n  <li>Analyze marketing campaigns to assess their impact on business growth.</li>\n  <li>Identify opportunities for process improvement based on data insights.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong>\n</p>\n\n<ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Business, Computer Science, Information Technology, Statistics, or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of experience working with data analysis, including SQL, ETL processes, and data modeling.</li>\n  <li>Strong proficiency in data visualization and reporting tools (e.g., Tableau, Power BI).</li>\n  <li>Ability to work collaboratively with stakeholders and communicate complex data insights clearly.</li>\n  <li>Excellent interpersonal and communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical and problem-solving skills with a detail-oriented mindset.</li>\n  <li>Ability to manage time efficiently and handle multiple tasks.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
