nd pipeline management to deal closing, ensuring revenue growth and improved conversion.</li>\n  <li>Manage 360° marketing activities, including campaigns, social media, community building, events, and paid ads, directly or with agencies.</li>\n  <li>Lead and develop cross-functional teams (Marketing, Sales, Data, Product) to achieve performance goals.</li>\n  <li>Own key growth metrics &amp; budgets, ensuring effective resource allocation, reporting to leadership, and continuous improvement of strategies.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Minimum 5 years of experience in Business Development, Sales, or Marketing, preferably in <strong>SaaS, IT System Integrator, or Tech Industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Proven track record in <strong>selling SaaS/technology solutions</strong> with long sales cycles and successful deal closures.</li>\n  <li>Proven experience in brand management and leading end-to-end marketing campaigns.</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of both digital and traditional media planning and execution.</li>\n  <li>Basic understanding of software implementation or IT/system integration is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Ability to analyze campaign data and optimize marketing efforts. </li>\n  <li>Demonstrated leadership skills with the ability to influence and align cross-functional stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Track record of delivering impactful brand communication initiatives in fast-paced environments.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>"}
